18#include <vector>
19#include <cstdint>
20
21namespace ZXing {
22
23/**
24 ByteArray is an extension of std::vector<unsigned char>.
25*/
26class ByteArray : public std::vector<uint8_t>
27{
28public:
29 ByteArray() = default;
30 ByteArray(std::initializer_list<uint8_t> list) : std::vector<uint8_t>(list) {}
31 explicit ByteArray(int len) : std::vector<uint8_t>(len, 0) {}
32};
33
34} // ZXing
